---
title: Spiced Beef & Currant Couscous with Yoghurt & Toasted Almonds
description: Our popular Aussie spice blend, with dried onion and garlic, instantly adds a rich, classic flavour to tender beef strips. Add sweet currants and veggies with a creamy yoghurt for a dish worth enjoying again and again.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
